after <strong>8:30 PM IST</strong> to complete your registration</li><li>Your partially filled form data has not been lost</li><li>Registration deadline remains <strong>18 May 2026</strong></li></ul></div><hr style=\"border:none;border-top:1px solid #f1f5f9;margin-bottom:24px\"/><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#94a3b8;line-height:1.8\">For urgent matters, contact the IEC at<!-- --> <strong style=\"color:#64748b\">alsiiec048@gmail.com</strong><br/><strong style=\"color:#64748b\">Independent Elections Commission (IEC)</strong><br/>Association of Liberian Students in India — General Elections 2026/2027</p></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"border-t bg-white\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-6\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-2 text-sm text-slate-500 md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between\"><p>© 2026 Independent Elections Commission (IEC) — ALSI</p><p>Official Election Registration Platform</p></div></div></footer></div><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/03tfhzrunrhlw.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script></body></html><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[7988,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/17qavn_yt9ecp.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0d3shmwh5_nmn.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n3:I[39756,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/17qavn_yt9ecp.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0d3shmwh5_nmn.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n4:I[37457,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/17qavn_yt9ecp.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0d3shmwh5_nmn.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n5:I[22016,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/17qavn_yt9ecp.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0d3shmwh5_nmn.js\\\"],\\\"\\\"]\\nd:I[68027,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/17qavn_yt9ecp.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0d3shmwh5_nmn.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\",1]\\n:HL[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/16.v4iiib-dg5.css\\\",\\\"style\\\"]\\n:HL[\\\"/_next/static/media/83afe278b6a6bb3c-s.p.0q-301v4kxxnr.woff2\\\",\\\"font\\\",{\\\"crossOrigin\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"font/woff2\\\"